snippet.title: Wanted: Dead - Valentine's Day Trailer
snippet.description:
This Valentine’s Day, 110 Industries comes bearing the appropriately red-hued gift that is the bloody new Wanted: Dead Valentine’s Day trailer. The trailer treats us to a closer look at the game’s stylish high-octane combat. Wanted: Dead is set to release in 2022.

Song: Inspector Mills by Bella & The Switchblades
